name: Weinstock Consulting
overview:
Weinstock Consulting has been helping companies fulfill their business management and information technology needs since 2004.

The Weinstock Consulting Team is comprised of individuals possessing diversified backgrounds in computerized business applications, operations, management, software, development, project/program management, and system engineering. This collective intelligence combined with broad technology skills enables Weinstock Consulting Team Members to assist clients in leveraging technology to improve their business processes and gain competitive advantage.

Weinstock Consulting is a Microsoft Gold Certified Partner with competencies in Microsoft Business Solutions, Advanced Infrastructure Solutions and Networking Infrastructure Solutions. Weinstock Consulting is located out of San Diego, California, but maintains a global reach by utilizing ever changing technology.
